{"root":{"data":{"id":"djqoc3waybk0","created":1783258374675,"text":"从智能手机获取的坐到站动作关节角速度可以作为有症状膝骨关节炎的时空标志"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djqogj1pdzc0","created":1783258721110,"text":"摘要"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djqoglbh6ug0","created":1783258726054,"text":"研究背景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djqol9eyaqo0","created":1783259091964,"text":"传统的运动捕捉技术虽然有效，但往往成本高昂且局限于实验室设置","layout_right_offset":{"x":-7.9999998807907104,"y":0}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqolt7xopc0","created":1783259135075,"text":"现有的可穿戴传感器和深度摄像头系统的进步使无监督运动评估更加可行，然而，这些技术仍然需要专门的硬件，限制了它们的广泛采用"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqolzrrjcg0","created":1783259149335,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djqogoow0kg0","created":1783258733396,"text":"研究发现"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djqogqz928g0","created":1783258738376,"text":"研究方向"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqogsr83yo0","created":1783258742244,"text":"实验方法"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqogv8xvxk0","created":1783258747669,"text":"研究结果"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqogxwcnbk0","created":1783258753438,"text":"创新点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djqoh0l1u7k0","created":1783258759285,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djqoh47nes80","created":1783258767182,"text":"总结"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djqoh5h7e6g0","created":1783258769936,"text":"缺陷"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djqoh822rwo0","created":1783258775552,"text":"展望"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}